---
title: Summer Corn and Chicken Pizza with Tomatoes, Scallions, and Adobo Sauce
description: Scallions are at the height of their flavor during the spring and summer months, which is why we find any excuse to sneak them into recipes for an extra pop of color and crisp oniony bite. Although this pizza carries a kick of heat, we’ve included a generous amount of creamy cheddar to balance it all out.
